Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.82,0:00:14.80,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\blur1\\pos(443.949,578.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:15.62,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.62,0:00:19.12,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:22.79,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:26.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.46,0:00:30.18,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.18,0:00:33.39,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.76,0:00:36.52,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.52,0:00:39.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:44.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:48.15,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.15,0:00:50.78,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:54.37,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.54,0:00:59.12,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:02.50,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.73,0:01:23.69,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HFCFFFE&\b1\pos(480.495,216.833)}The Eerie Spider Man
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.05,0:01:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.51,0:01:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not sure you'll win the grand\Nprix with times like this, Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a stickler,\NMr. Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.23,0:02:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go around again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll take ten more\Nseconds off my time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.15,0:02:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.70,0:02:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He can be such a child...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But he's a first-rate rider.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No one would believe he's\Nalso a leading scientist{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.12,0:02:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}at Johoku University's\Nbiochemistry lab.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Never seen them around before...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A challenge, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.40,0:02:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They're clearly after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.31,0:03:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to find out\Nwhat you're up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.33,0:04:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.21,0:04:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hongo Takeshi.\NWelcome to Shocker!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.84,0:04:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker?\NWhat is he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:42.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi heard\Nthe word "Shocker."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:44.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker is an evil\Norganization whose influence
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:46.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,stretches to all\Ncorners of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:49.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For some reason,\Nthey had brought Hongo Takeshi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.27,0:04:51.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to their secret base in\Na remote area of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:55.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker is a truly\Nterrifying organization,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:59.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,which plans to alter humans in\Ncountries all over the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.07,0:05:00.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and use them as pawns\Nfor global domination!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.95,0:05:08.58,Italics,,0,0,0,,We are seeking a man\Nwith an IQ of 600
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.58,0:05:11.33,Italics,,0,0,0,,and superior athleticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.75,0:05:15.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,You have the honor\Nof being chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I'll never join Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:23.09,Italics,,0,0,0,,It's too late to protest, Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:29.98,Italics,,0,0,0,,You are all but a member\Nof Shocker already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:34.56,Italics,,0,0,0,,It has been one week since you\Nwere brought here, unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:40.82,Italics,,0,0,0,,Shocker's scientists have used\Nthat time to alter your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:44.03,Italics,,0,0,0,,You are a cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:47.49,Italics,,0,0,0,,Cyborgs will control\Nthe fate of this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:51.29,Italics,,0,0,0,,and I will control the cyborgs!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:54.96,Italics,,0,0,0,,The world will be\Nmine to command!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Cyborgs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.05,0:06:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You expect me to believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:06.47,Italics,,0,0,0,,If you refuse to believe,\Nthen I will show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm about to channel 50,000\Nvolts through your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It would fry a normal man\Nto a crisp in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.72,0:06:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But your cyborg modifications have\Nimbued you with the power of wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Your body will not\Nsuffer a single burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The only reason you feel pain
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is because I have not completed\Nthe alterations to your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.59,0:07:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the brain alterations are complete,\Nand you become a slave to your orders...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you will be a\Ntrue cyborg of Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather die than serve you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what they all\Nsay, at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,In time, they become\Ngrateful to serve Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin the alterations\Nto Hongo Takeshi's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The generator's been destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Find the one\Nresponsible at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Midorikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure you'd gone missing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.26,0:08:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker is behind it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no... we have to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But how...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an exit above\Nus, through the ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.73,0:08:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't break through.\NIt's too high!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo. You snapped those\Niron chains effortlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.69,0:09:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an impossible act for a human...\Nbut you are a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ironically, Shocker's experiment to\Nimbue your body with the power of wind
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,has charged your body\Nwith devastating strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.37,0:09:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it now,\NI promise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no time to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Try it, Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He escaped out the ceiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo! Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.65,0:10:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.67,0:10:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All who betray Shocker must die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That includes your\Nonly daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.72,0:10:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-My daughter... Ruriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-Die, Midorikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:11:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't kill my daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.11,0:11:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:40.85,Bumper,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355,195)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:43.81,Bumper,,0,0,0,,{\\pos(355,195)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:48.19,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5CA4B9&\bord5}Johoku University\NSchool of Literature
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:11:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Ruriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.91,0:12:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You look kind of distracted...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anything wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hiromi...\Ndo you see anyone following me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being weird, Ruriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like someone's been watching\Nme these past three days...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Midorikawa's daughter Ruriko\Nand her friend have passed by.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Use the daughter to lure\Nout the good doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Where shall we strike?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,At the café where\NRuriko works...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.95,0:12:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Or on her way there, perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- There you are!\N- Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:12:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:12:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Scared of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw these strange men...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange men?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not nice to\Ntease your elders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Get on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you right to the café.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard your\Nfather's been found.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.44,0:13:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,My father?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the location.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.79,0:13:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The one that left in the car...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.37,0:14:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew my father was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,0:14:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Toura Pier, warehouse 50...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Toura Pier, warehouse 50...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.85,0:14:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, do you think I've\Ndone the right thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.31,0:14:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything were to\Nhappen to Ruriko, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You absolutely did\Nthe right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.57,0:14:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who can testify to\Nthe world about Shocker's terrible plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. I know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But I feel so powerless\Nto fight them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.25,0:14:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be doing everything I\Ncan, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I will fight to\Nliberate humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor... you must have\Nmore faith in yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor.\NYour daughter will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Buck up, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.43,0:15:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I have many times the\Nstrength of a normal man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can't control\Nit, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The cyborg part of me\Nthat's no longer human.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.91,0:16:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I remain a cyborg\Nfor the rest of my life?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, Hongo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all because I\Nchose you to help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You recommended me to Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.31,0:16:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is he arguing with?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.83,0:17:01.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,Someone who didn't know me might think\NI was an alien from a distant planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:02.96,Italics,,0,0,0,,But at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:07.88,Italics,,0,0,0,,The doctor and Mr. Tachibana\Nwill understand me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.57,0:17:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo! Can't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.45,0:17:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.59,0:17:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.93,0:17:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.68,0:17:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:17:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.42,0:18:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you strangle\Nmy father to death...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.13,0:18:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you want to save me? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.34,0:18:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'm not the\None who killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you arguing with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And I saw what I saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you kill my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet you still claim\Nit wasn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.90,0:18:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father and I\Nare on the same side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I will finish you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.22,0:22:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.93,0:22:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She's unconscious.\NPlease take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.49,0:23:09.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is putting his life\Non the line to fight Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:13.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Doctor Midorikawa,\Nwho understood him and helped him,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.75,0:23:15.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is now dead by Shocker's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.29,0:23:21.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And the doctor's only daughter, Ruriko,\Nbelieves Takeshi is the murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.76,0:23:25.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will he ever be able\Nto prove his innocence?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:32.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,More of Shocker's terrible\Nmonsters are waiting in the wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.94,0:23:40.75,Cont,,490,0,180,,{\blur.8\fad(0,350)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.94,0:23:42.58,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.36,0:23:45.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.90,0:23:47.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the terrifying Bat Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.95,0:23:51.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The monstrous Bat Man spreads his\Nterrifying virus among the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.87,0:23:55.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As sparks crackle in the night\Nsky, how will our Kamen Rider fare?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.54,0:23:57.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.50,0:24:00.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "The Terrifying Bat Man."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.80,0:24:10.64,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.22,0:24:13.22,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.22,0:24:15.18,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.18,0:24:18.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.73,0:24:20.61,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.61,0:24:22.44,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.44,0:24:24.28,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.28,0:24:25.61,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.07,0:24:28.11,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.16,0:24:33.83,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.83,0:24:37.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.41,0:24:41.00,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.50,0:24:45.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!